I"”<h2 id="solution">Solution:</h2>

<p>We apply the shifting technique to eliminate the history of the recurrence relation.</p>

\[\begin{align*}
        T(n + 1) - T(n) = \left[ (n + 1) + \sum_{i = 1}^{n}T(i) \right] - \left[ (n + 1) + \sum_{i = 1}^{n}T(i) \right]
        T(n) &amp;= n + \sum_{i = 1}^{n - 1}T(i) \\
        T(n + 1) &amp;= (n + 1) + \sum_{i = 1}^{n - 1}T(i)
    \end{align*}\]

\[\qed\]
